                    in all our wallpapers.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-12 lg:mt-16">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">
                    <div class="md:w-1/2">
                        <img
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center"
                            src="/images/componente-5.jpg"
                            alt="componente 5"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:w-1/2">
                        <div class="bg-gris-7 py-8 lg:py-16">
